description:
There are two backdrops for this story. Boggo Road Gaol and Samford.&#13;
One, a notorious Gaol that housed some of the most disturbed and violent offenders in Australian history, where many of these offenders met their end at the gallows.&#13;
The other, a small quiet farming town around a 30 minute drive from the Queensland capital of Brisbane.&#13;
Two very different places but one tragic incident would forge a connection between the two that would still be remembered over a century.&#13;
